Zimbabwe Magistrates Go on Strike for Higher Wages, Newsday Says

-- B y   N e l s o n   G o r e   B a n y a
-- 
2011-04-05T09:12:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/zimbabwe-magistrates-go-on-strike-for-higher-wages-newsday-says.html
Zimbabwe ’s magistrates went on
strike to press for higher wages, paralyzing operations at the
country’s lower courts, Harare-based Newsday reported, citing
the head of the court officials’ union, Douglas Chikwekwe.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nelson Gore Banya in Harare via Johannesburg at   ngbanya@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 